snippet.title: Whimside - Trailer Whishlist
snippet.description:
Whimside is a unique creature-collection game that sits at the bottom of your screen. Work, watch videos, or stream while capturing adorable creatures. Keep an eye out for rare whimlings, experiment with breeding, and explore new worlds while multitasking in this cozy and relaxing adventure!

Links:
* Website : https://www.whimside.com
* Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3064030/Whimside/
